data.text: @TimberWolff91 Was that for your 1st or 2nd? I was fine with my 1st dose, just a bit of shoulder pain for 2 days, but I've heard the 2nd dose is worse. I'm getting Moderna, so I don't get my 2nd until the 21st.
@SarahJBelcher83 Yay! Just FYI might be good to have someone drive you if you’re able - my reaction wasn’t bad but I was SO exhausted I slept for like 17 hours straight.
